    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Your little hero will be ready to save the day with the Kidplokio 360 Degree Bump and Go Emergency Responders! Whether it’s outside saving the neighborhood cat or extinguishing pretend play flames at a nearby fire, this set comes with a quick-moving fire truck or police car, making it the perfect action toy set ready to be first on the scene. An upgrade to this classic children’s toy, this fire truck toy is fitted with an extendable 360-degree rotating ladder, vibrant colors, realistic fire truck sirens, and can change directions upon contact with an object! The bump-and-go action allows the Fire truck to continually move even after hitting a wall, allowing the fun to never stop. It easily moves in all directions, forward, backward left, and right (x3 AA batteries needed but not included</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio 360 Degree Bump and Go Emergency Toys Fire Truck Police Car (2 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Your little hero will be ready to save the day with the Kidplokio 360 Degree Bump and Go Emergency Responders! Whether it’s outside saving the neighborhood cat or extinguishing pretend play flames at a nearby fire, this set comes with a quick-moving fire truck or police car, making it the perfect action toy set ready to be first on the scene.</p>\n  <p>An upgrade to this classic children’s toy, this fire truck toy is fitted with an extendable 360-degree rotating ladder, vibrant colors, realistic fire truck sirens, and can change directions upon contact with an object! The bump-and-go action allows the Fire truck to continually move even after hitting a wall, allowing the fun to never stop. It easily moves in all directions, forward, backward left, and right (x3 AA batteries needed but not included with purchase).</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>BUMP-AND-GO FIRST RESPONDERS:</strong> The fire truck or police car feature fun bump-and-go movement mechanisms, meaning if the cars bump into objects, they will recalibrate in a new direction and continue to drive! The toy rescue vehicles also feature vibrant flashing lights and realistic siren sounds</li>\n    <li><strong>VIBRANT LIGHTS AND SOUNDS:</strong> The bump-and-go toy cars feature bright lights and realistic siren sound effects, making playtime even more fun, engaging, realistic, and entertaining for little heroes on their way to rescue the neighborhood cat or put out flames at a nearby fire</li>\n    <li><strong>PRETEND PLAY RESCUE ADVENTURES:</strong> Both the police car and the fire truck are equipped with a 360-degree rotating feature for any daring rescue! Simply flip the power switch and watch their imagination soar as they create their own rescue adventures indoors or out (flat surface needed)</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE PLASTIC MATERIAL:</strong> Built to withstand bumps and minor crashes, the bump-and-go action cars are durable plastic and stand up to lots of playtime wear and tear! No other tools or accessories are needed for operation, making them easy and lightweight toys to tote when traveling with kids</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Weight: 2lbs; Batteries: x3 AA not included; Colors: Red (Fire truck), White (Police car); Ages: 3+</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/4493/police_car_fire_truck_bundle.jpg\" alt=\"Your little hero will be ready to save the day with the Kidplokio 360 Degree Bump and Go Emergency Responders\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ABCFRERTFTPC</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058485205</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The police car is fitted with cool car doors that open and close, as well as a back hatch that hovers open and closed; the police car also features cool police car coloring and marking, transparent wheels that light up, realistic siren sound effects, and even more flashing more lights, making playtime fun and exciting!</p>\n  <p>And, built to withstand bumps and minor crashes, these toy vehicles are made of durable plastic and will stand up to lots of playtime wear and tear! No other tools or accessories are needed for operation, making them an easy and lightweight toy tote option when traveling with kids.</p>\n  <p>Let the rescuing begin!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Your little hero will be ready to save the day with the Kidplokio 360 Degree Bump and Go Emergency Responders! Whether it’s outside saving the neighborhood cat or extinguishing pretend play flames at a nearby fire, this set comes with a quick-moving fire truck or police car, making it the perfect action toy set ready to be first on the scene. An upgrade to this classic children’s toy, this fire truck toy is fitted with an extendable 360-degree rotating ladder, vibrant colors, realistic fire truck sirens, and can change directions upon contact with an object! The bump-and-go action allows the Fire truck to continually move even after hitting a wall, allowing the fun to never stop. It easily moves in all directions, forward, backward left, and right (x3 AA batteries needed but not included.",
